      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以整个流程封装在一个叫\"OAuth 2.0 Model (Infra_WorkerNode)\"的子图里？起点是A节点的WorkerNode，它通过Login动作连到B节点的LoadBalancer？",
